WHAT ARE OUR PURPOSES FOR PROCESSING YOUR PERSONAL DATA?
We restrict the quantity and quality of the personal data we collect to what is strictly necessary for the purposes for which they are collected, as detailed in the table below. We restrict, protect, and monitor all our computer resources against unauthorised physical or electronic access,
  damage, loss, or destruction. We retain personal data exclusively for the periods of time detailed below, to respond to your requests, or longer if required by law. If we retain your personal data for historic or statistical purposes, we ensure that the personal data cannot be used for any
  other purposes. While in our possession, with your help, we endeavour to ensure that your personal data are accurate.
